              Once complete, we should have a website with interface kin to mainstream shopping site, but more importantly, a step to make cryptocurrency a viable option for commerce and not just finance tool for speculation. While people buying real commodities online with bitcoin directly isn't a new idea, it was first adopted by illegal operations like drugs and document forgery, we want crypto being used in day-to-day purchase.
